import {
  Container,
  Row,
  Col,
  Form,
  Button,
  Card,
  InputGroup,
  DropdownButton,
  Dropdown,
} from "react-bootstrap";

import React from "react";

export default function StoreCard({ store }) {
  return (
    <Card className="h-60">
      <Row>
        <Col xs={5}>
          <Card.Img
            variant="top"
            src={product.image}
            style={{ width: "100%" }}
          />
        </Col>
        <Col xs={7}>
          <Card.Body>
            <Card.Title>{product.name}</Card.Title>
            <Card.Text>{product.description}</Card.Text>
            <Card.Text>{product.rating} stars</Card.Text>
            <Card.Text>{product.store}</Card.Text>
            <Card.Text>{product.distance} miles from your location</Card.Text>
            <Card.Text>{product.location}</Card.Text>
            <Card.Text>${product.price}</Card.Text>
          </Card.Body>
        </Col>
      </Row>
    </Card>
  );
}
